---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Team - Neon Injector"
  description="Meet Agung, Andrian, and Ayu Sapitri, the dedicated team behind Neon Injector, committed to delivering innovative Mobile Legends skin customization and exceptional user support."
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <main class="flex-1 pt-16">
      <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-[var(--text-color)]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neon-purple mb-6 text-center">Meet Our Team</h1>
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg mb-6">At Neon Injector, our passionate team of innovators and gaming enthusiasts works tirelessly to enhance your Mobile Legends experience through cutting-edge skin customization and dedicated support. Led by our visionary CEO, Agung, and supported by our talented developer and community team, we combine technical expertise, creativity, and a commitment to player satisfaction. Get to know the brilliant minds behind Neon Injector and our mission to empower players worldwide.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- CEO Section -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <div class="bg-[var(--card-bg)] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-xl border border-neon-purple-dark max-w-md mx-auto text-center transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300">
            <img src="/team/agung-dev.webp" alt="CEO & Developer Agung" class="w-36 h-36 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover border-2 border-neon-purple" loading="lazy" />
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-neon-purple">Agung</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-neon-purple-light mt-1">CEO & Lead Developer</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">With over 12 years of Android development experience, Agung founded Neon Injector to revolutionize Mobile Legends skin customization. He leads the team with a focus on innovation, ensuring seamless compatibility, top-tier performance, and robust security across all Android devices. Agung’s vision is to create a tool that empowers players to express their style while respecting the integrity of the game.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Team Members Section -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-[var(--card-bg)] p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-neon-purple-dark text-center transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300">
            <img src="/team/andrian-dev.webp" alt="Developer Andrian" class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover border-2 border-neon-purple" loading="lazy" />
            <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-neon-purple">Andrian</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-neon-purple-light mt-1">Developer</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">Andrian is a skilled developer dedicated to optimizing Neon Injector’s core functionality. He focuses on enhancing injection speed, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of Android devices, and delivering a smooth user experience. His meticulous approach to coding and testing ensures that Neon Injector remains reliable and efficient for all players.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[var(--card-bg)] p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-neon-purple-dark text-center transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300">
            <img src="/team/ayu-dev.webp" alt="Admin Live Chat Ayu Sapitri" class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover border-2 border-neon-purple" loading="lazy" />
            <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-neon-purple">Ayu Sapitri</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-neon-purple-light mt-1">Admin Live Chat</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">Ayu Sapitri is our dedicated Admin Live Chat, providing real-time support to Neon Injector users. With her exceptional communication skills and deep knowledge of the app, she ensures that every user query is resolved promptly and effectively, fostering a supportive and engaged community.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-neon-purple mb-4">Our Commitment to Excellence</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">Under Agung’s leadership, our team is committed to pushing the boundaries of Mobile Legends customization. We continuously update Neon Injector to introduce new skins, improve performance, and incorporate feedback from our vibrant community. Our goal is to provide a tool that is not only functional but also safe and enjoyable. Join our <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Discord community</a> to share your ideas, report issues, or stay updated via our <a href="/blog" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Blog</a>.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-neon-purple mb-4 mt-8">Join Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">Are you passionate about gaming, technology, or community building? We’re always looking for talented developers, designers, and enthusiasts to join the Neon Injector team. Whether you’re skilled in Android development, UI/UX design, or community management, we’d love to hear from you. Reach out through our <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact page</a> or email us at <a href="mailto:support@neon-injector.my.id" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a> to explore collaboration opportunities.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-neon-purple mb-4 mt-8">Get Involved</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">Beyond development, we value our community’s input in shaping Neon Injector’s future. Share your favorite skins, suggest new features, or report bugs on our <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Discord server</a>. Stay informed about the latest updates, tutorials, and community events through our <a href="/blog" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Blog</a>. Together, we can make Neon Injector the ultimate tool for Mobile Legends customization.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>